description:
Will is adorably dorky!

He looks like he could be an underwear model... tall, lean, tan, and good looking. But when he speaks it’s a totally different story. He has this midwest/southern accent, with a very down-home way of explaining everything.

He says he loves boxing and that he’s been doing it for about five years. He gave us a little demonstration... and it was, well, unpolished. But he tried and I enjoyed just watching him do it.

I bet that he’s very shy around girls. He’s soft spoken and doesn’t seem like the party type.

He’s finishing up his four-year degree and he says he can’t wait to be done.

“It’s been a lot of work,” he said. “But I’m almost there!”
title: Will
